00:51:24.180 --> 00:51:29.730
Neil, do you want to
just make a few comments,

00:51:29.730 --> 00:51:31.310
or whatever you want to do.

00:51:33.422 --> 00:51:35.880
NEIL LEONARD: How many people
have done something like this

00:51:35.880 --> 00:51:37.340
before?

00:51:37.340 --> 00:51:39.990
Anybody?

00:51:39.990 --> 00:51:41.720
And suddenly you've
done Ableton Live.

00:51:41.720 --> 00:51:43.810
And how many people
have done Ableton Live?

00:51:43.810 --> 00:51:44.740
One, two.

00:51:44.740 --> 00:51:47.611
So, what have you done
with Ableton Live before?

00:51:47.611 --> 00:51:51.940
AUDIENCE: [INAUDIBLE] Just
learning how to use it.

00:51:51.940 --> 00:51:54.665
I really haven't
